ana Das]] || || |- | ''[[Abhinetri (Oriya film)|Abhinetri]]'' || [[Amar Ganguly]] ||[[Umakant]], [[Jharana Das]] || || |- | ''[[Malajanha]]''||[[Nitai Palit]]||[[Akshaya Mohanty]], [[Jharana Das]] || || |- | ''[[Jeevan Sathi]]''||[[Prabhat Mukherjee]]||[[Prashanta Nanda]], [[Meenati]]|||| |- | ''[[Bhagya]]''||[[Amar Ganguly]]||[[Gaura Ghosh]] |||| |- | {{Year header}} | '''[[1966 in film|1966]]''' |- | ''[[Kaa (film)|Kaa]]'' ||[[Sidharth (director)|Sidharth]] ||[[Gaur Ghosh]], [[Chandana Banerjee|Chandana]] ||Family drama ||Based on Kanhu charan Mohanty's novel by the same name |- | ''[[Matira Manisha]]''||[[Mrinal Sen]]||[[Prashanta Nanda]], [[Sarat Pujari]], [[Sujata Anand]], Bhanumati Devi||Social drama set in rural Odisha ||National Award Silver lotus for Best Odia Film; based on Kalindi Charan Panigrahi's novel by the same title |- | {{Year header}} | '''[[1967 in film|1967]]''' |- | ''[[Bhai Bhauja]]'' ||[[Sarathi]] ||[[Babi (actress)|Babi]], [[Manimala (Actress)|Manimala]] || || |- | ''[[Arundhati (1967 film)|Arundhati]]''||[[Prafulla Sengupta]] ||[[Sarat Pujari]], [[Minati]] || || |- | {{Year header}} | '''[[1968 in film|1968]]''' |- | ''[[Kie Kahara]]'' ||[[Nitai Palit]]||[[Sarat Pujari]], [[Leela (actress)|Leela]]|| || |- | ''[[Stree (1968 film)|Stree]]'' ||[[Sidharth (director)|Sidharth]]||[[Gaur Ghosh]], [[Sadhana Shivdasani|Sadhana]]|| || |- | {{Year header}} | '''[[1969 in film|1969]]''' |- | ''[[Bandhana (Odia film)|Bandhan]]'' ||[[Nitai Palit]] ||[[Prashanta Nanda]], [[Geetanjali (actress)|Geetanjali]] || || |- | ''[[Adina Megha]]'' || [[Amit Mitra (director)|Amit Mitra]] ||[[Prashanta Nanda]], [[Jharana Das]], [[Sandhya (Odia actress)|Sandhya]] || || |}
