ar]]||[[Sambit]], [[Suprena Singh]], [[Harihar]]|| ||6 May 2011|| |- | ''[[Anjali (Oriya film)|Anjali]]''||[[Biswa Bhusan Mohapatra]] ||[[Aditya]], [[Sampurna Chakraborty]], [[Deabasmitha]], [[Raj (South Indian actor)|Raj]]|| ||20 May 2011|| |- | ''[[Family No.1 (Oriya film)|Family No.1]]''||[[Nishikant Dalabehera]] ||[[Deepak]], Subhangi, Subhangi, [[Chaudhury Bikash das]], [[Biju badjena]]||Drama, romance ||27 May 2011|| |- | ''[[Kie Se Dekuchi Kouthi Mote (Oriya film)|Kie se Dekuchi Kouthi Mote]]'' ||[[Sudhakar Basanta]] ||[[Anubhav Mohanty]], [[Barsa Priyadarshini]], [[Bijay Mohanty]], Somesh ||Action, Drama, Romance || 14 June 2011|| |- | ''[[143 I Love You (Oriya film)|143 I Love You]]'' ||[[Ashok Pati]] ||[[Siddhanta Mahapatra]], [[Babu San]], [[Namrata Thapa]], [[Koel Banarjee]], [[Mihir Das]], [[Samresh Routaray]], [[Minaketan]], [[Harihara]], [[Pintu Nanda]] || Action, Drama, Romance || 14 June 2011|| |- | ''[[Baisi Pahache Kheliba Mina ... Pralaya asuchi (Oriya film)|Baisi Pahache Kheliba Mina ... Pralaya asuchi]]'' ||[[Sanjay Nayak]] ||Lalit, [[Poonam Mishra]], [[Bijay Mohanty]], [[Mihir Das]], [[Priya Choudhary]], Bina Moharana || || 14 June 2011|| |- | ''[[Chori Chori Mana Chori (Oriya film)|Chori Chori Mana Chori]]'' ||[[Rajib Mohanty]] || Debasish Patra, Nikita, Meena Ketan, Pintu Nanda, Puspa Panda, Snigdha ||Action, Drama, Romance || 29 July 2011| | Remake of Hindi film ''Baaghi: A Rebel for Love'', starring Salman Khanand& Nagma |- | ''[[Chocolate (Oriya film)|Chocolate]]'' ||[[Susant Mani]] || Babusaan, Archita, Aparajita Mohanty, Samaresh || Drama, romance || 7 August 2011||Inspired by the English movie ''[[A Walk to Remember]]'' |- | ''[[Mane Rahiba Ae Prema Kahani (Oriya film)|Mane Rahiba Ae Prema Kahani]]'' ||[[Narayan Ghadei]] || Rupali, Rudra, Asrumochan Mohanty, Samaresh || Action, drama, romance ||August, 2011 || Remake of Telgu movie ''Antena'', starring Siba Sankar Pattnaik, Iliana D. Cruz |- | ''[[Dosti (Oriya film)|Dosti]]'' ||[[Ashok