y|Arindam]],Sheetal Patra |Romance, Comedy |2016 |[[Sarthak Music Pvt. Ltd.]] | |- |[http://www.odiahits.com/odia-film/samaya-bada-balaban-2016/ Samaya Bada Balaban] |S.K. Muralidharan
