{{Infobox language |name=Metombola |nativename= |states=[[Gabon]] |region= |speakers=? |date= |ref= |familycolor=Niger-Congo |fam2=[[Atlantic–Congo languages|Atlantic–Congo]] |fam3=[[Benue–Congo languages|Benue–Congo]] |fam4=[[Bantoid languages|Bantoid]] |fam5=[[Bantu languages|Bantu]] ([[Guthrie classification of Bantu languages#Zone B|Zone B]]) |fam6=[[Kele languages|Kele]] (b. 20) |iso3=none |glotto=none |guthrie=B.205 }} '''Metombola''' is a minor [[Bantu language]] of [[Gabon]].
