===Kinship Terms=== {| class="wikitable" |nakne |man, male |- |ooche |son |- |ooshtayke |daughter |- |táàte |father |- |tayke |woman, female |- |wáàche |mother |- |yaate |person |- |yaatooche |infant |- |}
